description: Welcome to The Residences at 527 East 7th Street!—South Boston’s newest boutique development with just 8 exclusive homes. This newly constructed East Side 3-bedroom duplex offers garage parking, TWO living rooms, and high-end finishes throughout. Designed by Louis Ashman, each unit blends modern elegance with top-tier craftsmanship. The main level features an open living area with a gas fireplace, dining nook and two bedrooms, while the lower level offers a second living room with fireplace, built-in bar, and a third bedroom. The kitchen boasts Thermador appliances, Quartz countertops, and custom cabinetry. Enjoy the convenience of deeded garage parking, private storage, and additional parking available for sale. Situated in one of South Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods, this boutique building offers luxury, comfort, and prime location!
